vote.title:
Authorize contracts with cultural organizations for the provision of artist services to the City through the Cultural Organizations Program for the period October 1, 2025 through September 30, 2026 (list attached to Agenda Information Sheet) - Not to exceed $7,164,665.00 - Financing: General Fund

*In alignment with Cultural Plan.
